OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Frain soon clearing the far east.
OL,7,FOtherwise it will be dry and clear
OL,8,Fthrough the evening and overnight
OL,9,Fallowing a quite widespread frost to
OL,10,Fdevelop.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FIt will be a cold start with
OL,13,Fsome frost on Friday, then a dry and
OL,14,Fsunny day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
