OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright on Saturday, clouding over
OL,7,Flater. Variable cloud and bright
OL,8,Fspells on Sunday, cloudier with rain
OL,9,Fspreading east later, clearing Monday
OL,10,Fmorning, then becoming dry with some
OL,11,Fbrightness.
